title: Studio Apt-Bryant Towers--available September 1
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Hornig Companies |  Jay', 'show contact info', 'Please contact us for a virtual tour or an in-person tour.', 'Photos are not from this apartment but are from a similar one in the building.', 'Studio/1BA', 'Uptown/Wedge/Lowry Hill East', '2001 Bryant Ave S #208', '$855/monthly', 'KEY FEATURES', '________________________________________', 'Year Built: 1965', 'Bedrooms: 0', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Sq Footage: approx.', '400', 'Parking: Heated Underground Garage @ $95/monthly, please inquire for availability', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year (6 and 9 month leases available for an additional fee.)', 'Deposit: $500.00', 'App Fee: $45 per adult (returning Hornig residents get waived application fee)', 'Pets Policy: Cat Friendly, no dogs or caged animals (ask for details)', 'Laundry:', 'In Building on each floor', 'Utilities: Included in rent- Gas/heat, Trash/Recycling', 'Resident Responsibility- Electricity and Water /Sewer', 'DESCRIPTION', '________________________________________', 'Location is everything and this ones got it.', '2001 Bryant Ave South is located only a block off Hennepin on the corner of Franklin and Bryant!', 'Within walking distance of the grocery, restaurants, night life and many other attractions - convenient to both Uptown and Downtown, and is only steps from public transportation.', 'The kitchens and bathrooms have been updated, and most apartments have newer carpet and/or vinyl, as well as some new appliances.', 'RENTAL FEATURES', '________________________________________', '- Open living room/dining room floor plan', '- Great closet space', '- Electric stove/oven', '- Refrigerator', '- Cable-Ready/High Speed Fiber Optic Internet Ready', '- Additional Storage available', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '________________________________________', '- Controlled access', '- Bike storage', '- Heated Underground Garage Parking', '- Close to many destinations', 'Apply online at <URL>', 'Managed by Hornig Companies']
